{
  "stem": "27340.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's quite nice to look at.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when in London, I, I, I became very active in the Habonim movement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And ultimately, that led me to be asked whether I would be prepared to undertake something a little bit more serious and strenuous than just running a, a, a, a youth movement with a Zionist ideology and then socialist views.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, yes, certainly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anything that could be of value would be accepted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so ultimately I was drafted into an organization that was possibly called Haganah in Europe-- I don't know what the official title of it was-- an organization that dealt fundamentally with illegal immigration into Palestine.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are now in 1946, summer of 1946.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I was sworn into this organization, absolutely forced to total and complete secrecy and everything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I heard nothing more about the whole thing for about nine months until one day I was being advised that I have to hold myself ready to undertake some strenuous duties, I think they called it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This might take anything up to six months, and it certainly wouldn't be in London.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'd have to leave everything behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By everything, I meant my job as a junior draftsman, my activities in the youth movement, and certainly my part-time studies at the university, because I was trying to gain qualifications as an engineer, having had some very good practical experience as an apprentice through my career.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I mentioned this to my parents, that I would not be available for some period of time, my father almost fell off his chair.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, [SPEAKING GERMAN], you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can you throw overboard your social ties, your family-- meaning himself and my mother-- and particularly your studies?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
